Nuxii 

https://nuxii.fr/

https://nuxii.fr/index.php?id_product=71&controller=product&id_lang=1


see IR commands with:
irw



In Debian 

Add the following to /boot/config.txt:

dtoverlay=lirc-rpi
dtparam=gpio_in_pin=25

copy nuxii's lircd.conf in:

/home/user/.config/lircd.conf




In LibreELEC

Add the following to /flash/config.txt

dtoverlay=lirc-rpi,gpio_in_pin=18

copy nuxii's lircd.conf in:
/storage/.config/lircd.conf




In piCorePlayer - incomplete

Install lirc from webui

in PCP parttion add following to /config.txt

dtoverlay=lirc-rpi,gpio_in_pin=18
